n of the magnetic field structure and gas\ndynamics, in particular the role of magnetic fields in gas outflows, as well as\nthe possible heating of DIG by magnetic reconnection.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 13 Oct 2000 16:07:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
